title: The ‘Better Call Saul’ Series Finale
description:
Chris and Andy talk about the series finale of ‘Better Call Saul.’ They talk about whether or not the creators stuck the landing (1:00), the major plot points that were revealed in the finale (14:57), and the feat of long-form storytelling that is ‘Breaking Bad’ and ‘Better Call Saul’ (37:59).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Producer: Kaya McMullen
